name: NEW YEAR'S EVE 2014
description:
DJ B-Mello will do a guest appearance & spin at your event for up to 2 hours on New Year's Eve.  

Travel & accomodations included.

name: Live Event Booking. DJ B-Mello for OVERSEAS (includes airfare)
description:
DJ B-Mello will fly in to your city or town and perform at a club, show, or event. 
The performance will be anywhere from 1-2 hours long. 
AIRFARE & HOTEL IS INCLUDED IN THE PRICE.
DJ B-Mello will be available for a 30 minute meet n greet on the day of the show if requested. 
A technical rider of equipment will be provided when booking is complete. 
This is available for venues outside of the USA

name: Live Event Booking. DJ B-Mello for 2 hours!
description:
DJ B-Mello will fly in to your city or town and perform at a club, show, or event.
The performance will be anywhere from 1-2 hours long.
DJ B-Mello will be available for a 30 minute meet n greet on the day of the show if requested.
A technical rider of equipment will be provided when booking is complete.
This is only available within the USA.
This includes airfare & hotel.

name: Custom DJ B-MELLO Hosted Mixtape
description:
DJ B-Mello will host your mixtape.
You provide the tracks (up to 60 minutes total).
You will receive custom shout outs from DJ B-Mello provided you provide a drop script.
DJ B-Mello will blast your mixtape to his digital networks including Twitter, Facebook, & his blogs.
Price reduction available for multiple mixtapes.
You are responsible for the pressing of physical CDs
Allow 2-3 weeks for the turnaround.

name: Artist Slot on Independent Heat Vol. 4
description:
Placement of your original track on DJ B-Mello "Independent Heat Vol. 4" which will be available for FREE download on June 1st, 2012.  

Your logo will also be included along with the sponsor logos on the CD insert artwork which will be promoted along with the release.  

You will receive 20 physical CD copies of the project to do as you choose with.
